fields.name: Martin D-28
fields.short_description: A legendary dreadnought with rich bass, powerful projection, and classic tonewoods like Sitka spruce and East Indian rosewood. Ideal for professionals and serious enthusiasts.

fields.name: Taylor 214ce
fields.short_description: A Grand Auditorium acoustic-electric with layered rosewood back and sides, solid Sitka spruce top, and Taylor’s ES2 pickup system. Great for versatile playing styles.

fields.name: Yamaha FG800
fields.short_description: Solid spruce top, nato back/sides and scalloped bracing make this a perfect first serious acoustic.

fields.name: Fender CD-60S
fields.short_description: Affordable dreadnought with a solid spruce top and a warm, balanced tone. Great for beginners.

fields.name: Gibson J-45 Standard
fields.short_description: The iconic round-shoulder dreadnought known for its deep bass and warm mids.

fields.name: Epiphone Hummingbird Studio
fields.short_description: A stylish and affordable tribute to the classic Gibson Hummingbird. Features onboard electronics.

fields.name: Takamine GD30CE
fields.short_description: Solid spruce top with mahogany back and sides, cutaway and onboard preamp system.

fields.name: Breedlove Discovery Concert CE
fields.short_description: Eco-friendly design with a comfortable neck and great tone for light strumming and fingerstyle.

fields.name: Seagull S6 Original
fields.short_description: Made in Canada with a cedar top and wild cherry back and sides, offering rich, mellow tone.

fields.name: Ibanez AW54CE
fields.short_description: Solid mahogany top dreadnought with a warm, earthy tone. Cutaway and electronics included.

fields.name: Martin LX1 Little Martin
fields.short_description: Compact and travel-friendly with a solid spruce top and HPL body. A perfect couch or travel guitar.

fields.name: Taylor GS Mini Mahogany
fields.short_description: A portable and playable guitar with great tone, thanks to its solid mahogany top.

fields.name: Yamaha APX600
fields.short_description: Thin-line body with cutaway and ART pickup. Ideal for players who perform live.

fields.name: Fender FA-125
fields.short_description: An ultra-budget-friendly acoustic that still delivers dependable tone and feel.

fields.name: Gibson G-45 Studio
fields.short_description: American-made solid wood guitar that brings modern tone and comfort to a classic body.

fields.name: Epiphone DR-100
fields.short_description: A classic Epiphone dreadnought with great projection and a very approachable price.

fields.name: Takamine GN93CE
fields.short_description: Beautifully crafted guitar with solid top and 3-piece back design, great for stage and studio.

fields.name: Breedlove Pursuit Exotic Concert CE
fields.short_description: Exotic wood choices and onboard electronics for stage-ready tones.

fields.name: Seagull Entourage Rustic
fields.short_description: Canadian-built, cedar top, and wild cherry back for a warm and vintage-inspired voice.

fields.name: Ibanez PF15
fields.short_description: Solid starter dreadnought with great playability and construction for the price.

fields.name: Guild D-55
fields.short_description: High-end dreadnought with solid tonewoods and powerful voice. A pro-level instrument.

fields.name: Washburn WD7S
fields.short_description: Affordable solid-top dreadnought with smooth playability and classic tone.

fields.name: Larrivée D-40R
fields.short_description: Handcrafted quality with all-solid wood construction and pristine tone.

fields.name: Faith Neptune
fields.short_description: Mid-sized body with solid wood tone and British hand-crafted design.

fields.name: Blueridge BR-143
fields.short_description: Vintage styling and tone. Perfect for folk and bluegrass lovers seeking authenticity.
